---
layout: base.njk
title: Our Sponsors
description: Thank you to our generous sponsors who make the Central Utah Tree Festival possible. Learn how your business can become a sponsor and support families in Sanpete County.
keywords: Central Utah Tree Festival sponsors, business sponsorship, Sanpete County support, community partners
givebutter: true
---

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="sponsors-hero">
    <h1>Our Sponsors</h1>
    <p>
        Thank you to our generous sponsors and community partners who make our mission possible.
        Together, we're helping families access the care their children need.
    </p>
</section>

<div class="sponsors-container">
    <!-- Introduction -->
    <div class="sponsors-intro">
        <h2>Community Partnership</h2>
        <p>{{ sponsors.intro }}</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Sponsor Tiers -->
    {% for tier in sponsors.tiers %}
    <div class="sponsor-tier">
        <div class="tier-header">
            <h2 class="tier-title">{{ tier.name }}</h2>
            <p class="tier-description">{{ tier.contribution }}</p>
        </div>

        {% if tier.sponsors.length > 0 %}
        <div class="sponsor-logos">
            {% for sponsor in tier.sponsors %}
            <div class="sponsor-logo">
                {% if sponsor.logo %}
                <img src="{{ sponsor.logo }}" alt="{{ sponsor.name }}" loading="lazy">
                {% else %}
                <p>{{ sponsor.name }}</p>
                {% endif %}
                {% if sponsor.url %}
                <a href="{{ sponsor.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit Website</a>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        {% else %}
        <div class="sponsor-placeholder">
            <h3>{{ sponsors.placeholders[tier.level].title }}</h3>
            <p>{{ sponsors.placeholders[tier.level].text }}</p>
            <a href="/contact/" class="sponsor-cta">Learn More</a>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endfor %}

    <!-- Become a Sponsor Section -->
    <section class="become-sponsor">
        <h2>Become a Sponsor</h2>
        <p>
            Your business can make a real difference in the lives of families throughout Sanpete County.
            Sponsorship with the Central Utah Tree Festival demonstrates your commitment to community health
            and family support while gaining valuable visibility and recognition.
        </p>

        <div class="sponsor-benefits">
            <div class="benefit-item">
                <h3>Platinum Benefits</h3>
                <ul>
                    {% for benefit in sponsors.tiers[0].benefits %}
                    <li>{{ benefit }}</li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item">
                <h3>Gold Benefits</h3>
                <ul>
                    {% for benefit in sponsors.tiers[1].benefits %}
                    <li>{{ benefit }}</li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item">
                <h3>Silver & Bronze Benefits</h3>
                <ul>
                    {% for benefit in sponsors.tiers[2].benefits %}
                    <li>{{ benefit }}</li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">
            <strong>All sponsorships are tax-deductible.</strong><br>
            Central Utah Tree Festival is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization.
        </p>

        <a href="/contact/" class="sponsor-cta">Contact Us About Sponsorship</a>
    </section>
</div>
